A_418 - More or less powerful missiles can be used for mining purposes. By hitting some mountains correctly (after having carried out all the necessary calculations and choosing places where there are as few life forms as possible and when possible moving them) it is possible to obtain rocky material which can subsequently be worked and processed more easily to extract certain minerals or even simple stone from use for the most varied purposes. They should not be used for war purposes. Alternatively they can also be used in deserts or barren plains. I also recommend surrounding the instrument with potted plants before carrying out the operation and removing them once the operation is completed. However, it is important to make audiovisual recordings to disseminate and have it used only by qualified personnel (e.g. from the army and the companies involved).